msgid "The <command>ln -s <replaceable>target</replaceable> <replaceable>link-name</replaceable></command> command creates a symbolic link, named <replaceable>link-name</replaceable>, pointing to <replaceable>target</replaceable>."
msgstr "Perintah <command>ln -s <replaceable>target</replaceable> <replaceable>nama-tautan</replaceable></command> membuat tautan simbolis, bernama <replaceable>nama-tautan</replaceable>, menunjuk ke <replaceable>target</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
